{
  "format_version": "1.17",
  "minecraft:npc_dialogue": {
    "scenes": [
      {
        "scene_tag": "blacksmith.root",
        "npc_name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§cBrenna Ironsong, Blacksmith§r" }] },
        "on_open_commands": ["/playsound random.anvil_land @initiator ~ ~ ~ 0.3"],
        "text": {
          "rawtext": [
            {
              "text": "Mind the sparks. I'm Brenna — I keep this village in nails, hinges, and the occasional sword nobody hopes to use.\n\nYou're the one they're calling the Awoken? Hmph. Prophecies don't hold a shield wall. §oSteel§r does. But my forge is cold more days than not... unless you can feed it."
            }
          ]
        },
        "buttons": [
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§eWhy did you come to Elderfall?§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/dialogue open @s @initiator blacksmith.lore"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§eHow can I help the forge?§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/dialogue open @s @initiator blacksmith.quests"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§eShow me what the forge sings.§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/dialogue open @s @initiator blacksmith.shop"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "Stay sharp, Brenna." }] },
            "commands": ["/dialogue close @s @initiator"]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "scene_tag": "blacksmith.lore",
        "npc_name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§cBrenna Ironsong, Blacksmith§r" }] },
        "text": {
          "rawtext": [
            {
              "text": "I was an armorer in the lowland wars. Forged blades for men who broke them on each other. When my company was routed, I walked north until the fighting was a rumor, and Elderfall took me in without asking what my hammer had made.\n\nHere's the thing no one tells you about the ruins: iron pulled from this soil §osings§r on the anvil. High and clear, like a struck bell. My grandmother would've called it blessed. I call it good ore. Either way — what I forge from it does not miss."
            }
          ]
        },
        "buttons": [
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "Back." }] },
            "commands": ["/dialogue open @s @initiator blacksmith.root"]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "scene_tag": "blacksmith.quests",
        "npc_name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§cBrenna Ironsong, Blacksmith§r" }] },
        "text": {
          "rawtext": [
            {
              "text": "Two jobs, if your spine's straight enough.\n\n§6Embers of the Forge§r — bring me §f16 iron ingots§r and I'll get this forge roaring again. The village pays in emeralds; I pay in gratitude and free repairs.\n\n§6Hold the Line§r — once the forge burns, I need proof the Corrupted can bleed. Put down §f10 Corrupted Raiders§r and the first blade off my anvil is yours: the §bElderfall Defender's Blade§r, sung from ruin-iron."
            }
          ]
        },
        "buttons": [
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§aAccept: Embers of the Forge§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/scriptevent lore:quest accept embers_of_the_forge"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§bTurn in: Embers of the Forge§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/scriptevent lore:quest turnin embers_of_the_forge"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§aAccept: Hold the Line§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/scriptevent lore:quest accept hold_the_line"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§bMy quest log.§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/scriptevent lore:quest status"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "Back." }] },
            "commands": ["/dialogue open @s @initiator blacksmith.root"]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "scene_tag": "blacksmith.shop",
        "npc_name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§cBrenna Ironsong, Blacksmith§r" }] },
        "text": {
          "rawtext": [
            {
              "text": "Ruin-iron, every one — quenched singing. Emeralds keep the coal coming:\n\n§6Emberfang§r — sets what it bites on fire — §a24§r\n§bFrostbite§r — chills foes to a crawl — §a24§r\n§3Wardenspike§r — every strike hardens YOUR hide — §a28§r\n§9Stormcall§r — sometimes the sky answers it — §a40§r\n\nThe rest of my racks? Earned, not sold. Ask about work."
            }
          ]
        },
        "buttons": [
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§aBuy: Emberfang (24)§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/scriptevent lore:shop buy blade_emberfang"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§aBuy: Frostbite (24)§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/scriptevent lore:shop buy blade_frostbite"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§aBuy: Wardenspike (28)§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/scriptevent lore:shop buy blade_wardenspike"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "§aBuy: Stormcall (40)§r" }] },
            "commands": ["/scriptevent lore:shop buy blade_stormcall"]
          },
          {
            "name": { "rawtext": [{ "text": "Back." }] },
            "commands": ["/dialogue open @s @initiator blacksmith.root"]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
